OL,3,CMan charged with rape and
OL,4,Cintentionally transmitting HIV
OL,6,FA man has appeared in court in South
OL,7,FTyneside charged with multiple counts
OL,8,Fof rape, and accused of intentionally
OL,9,Ftransmitting HIV.
OL,11,FAdam Hall, aged 42 of no fixed abode
OL,12,Fbut previously of the Washington area
OL,13,Ffaces five counts of rape relating to
OL,14,Ffive males and seven counts of causing
OL,15,Fgrievous bodily harm, relating to the
OL,16,Ftransmission of HIV.
OL,18,FHall is also charged with two counts
OL,19,Fof controlling or coercive behaviour
OL,20,Fand one count of supplying the Class B
OL,21,Fdrug GHB.
