OL,6,FFollowing his appearance at South
OL,7,FTyneside Magistrates Court on
OL,8,FWednesday 4 June, Hall was remanded in
OL,9,Fcustody and is due to appear before
OL,10,FNewcastle Crown Court on 2 July.
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Emma Smith,
OL,13,Ffrom Northumbria Police, said:
OL,14,F"Following a significant
OL,15,Finvestigation, an individual has been
OL,16,Fcharged with multiple counts of rape
OL,17,Fand other extremely serious offences.
