OL,6,F"We recognise the nature of the
OL,7,Fcharges may raise concern and anxiety
OL,8,Fwithin our communities. We would
OL,9,Fencourage anyone who does have
OL,10,Fconcerns or believes they have
OL,11,Finformation which is relevant to this
OL,12,Fcase to come forward.
OL,14,F"With criminal proceedings now active
OL,15,Fwe would also remind people that it is
OL,16,Fimportant to avoid speculation, both
OL,17,Fonline and in our communities, as this
OL,18,Fcould impact the case."
